'''安普瓜社区学院枪击案'''在2015年10月1日发生于在[[美国|美国]][[俄勒冈州|俄勒冈州]][[罗斯堡_(俄勒冈州)|罗斯堡]]北部6千米的{{le|安普瓜社区学院|Umpqua Community College}}。26岁的枪手克里斯·哈珀·梅瑟（{{lang|en|Chris Harper Mercer}}）<ref name="CBSAP">{{cite news|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/news/oregon-community-college-shooting-umpqua-community-college-roseburg/|title=Oregon shooting: Umpqua Community College in Roseburg site of deadly rampage|date=2015-10-01|publisher=CBS News|accessdate=2015-10-02|archive-date=2020-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201206172008/https://www.cbsnews.com/news/oregon-community-college-shooting-umpqua-community-college-roseburg/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=KTLA.Enrolled>{{cite web|url=http://ktla.com/2015/10/01/umpqua-community-college-shooter-targeted-christians-father-of-oregon-shooting-victim-says/|title=Oregon Gunman Was Enrolled in Class Where He Opened Fire, Authorities Say|work=KTLA|date=2015-10-02|accessdate=2015-10-02|first=Mary Beth|last=McDade|first2=Eric|last2=Spillman}}</ref>开枪打死9人，弄伤7人，之后在与警方的枪战中被击毙<ref name=ibtimes>{{cite web | url=http://www.ibtimes.com/who-chris-harper-mercer-oregons-alleged-umqua-community-college-shooter-identified-2123675 | title=Who Is Chris Harper Mercer? Oregon's Alleged Umqua [sic] Community College Shooter Identified, Police Say | work=IBTimes | date=2015-10-01 | accessdate=2015-10-01 | archive-date=2015-10-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151002234847/http://www.ibtimes.com/who-chris-harper-mercer-oregons-alleged-umqua-community-college-shooter-identified-2123675 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=KOIN.Among>{{cite web|url=http://koin.com/2015/10/01/active-shooter-reported-at-umpqua-community-college/|title=Gunman among 10 dead at Umpqua Community College|publisher=KOIN|date=2015-10-01|accessdate=2015-10-01|archive-date=2015-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151002061934/http://koin.com/2015/10/01/active-shooter-reported-at-umpqua-community-college/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Ford/><ref name=NBC>{{cite news|last1=Ortiz|first1=Erik|last2=Johnson|first2=M. Alex|last3=Winter|first3=Tom|title=13 Killed in Shooting at Oregon's Umpqua Community College: Officials|url=http://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/officers-respond-report-shooting-umpqua-community-college-n437051|accessdate=2015-10-01|publisher=NBC News|date=2015-10-01|archive-date=2015-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151001215805/http://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/officers-respond-report-shooting-umpqua-community-college-n437051|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=KGW.Shooting/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://abcnews.go.com/US/multiple-casualties-shooting-reported-college-oregon/story?id=34181664|title=Male Shooter at Umpqua Community College Dead, Sheriff Says|publisher=ABC News|date=2015-10-01|accessdate=2015-10-01|archive-date=2021-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210220153906/https://abcnews.go.com/US/multiple-casualties-shooting-reported-college-oregon/story?id=34181664|dead-url=no}}</ref>。本案是俄勒冈州史上伤亡最惨重的大规模枪击案<ref name=KGW.Shooting/>。

== 背景 ==
事发地安普瓜社区学院位于[[俄勒冈州|俄勒冈州]][[罗斯堡_(俄勒冈州)|罗斯堡]]北部{{convert|6|mi|km}}处，16间校舍占地{{Convert|100|acre|ha}}，与北安普瓜河接壤<ref name=GNIS>{{cite gnis |id= 1135783 |name= Umpqua Community College |entrydate= 1991-11-01 |accessdate= 2015-10-01}}</ref>。园区还设有跑道、网球场和一个室外游泳池，2009年新增了葡萄园，3300名全日制学生和16000名兼职学生就读于该校<ref name=UCCInformation>{{cite web |url=http://www.umpqua.edu/current-students/catalog |title=Umpqua Community College Catalog, 2010–2011 |accessdate=2010-11-15 |author=Umpqua Community College |year=2010 |publisher=Umpqua Community College |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101126122315/http://www.umpqua.edu/current-students/catalog |archivedate=2010-11-26 }}</ref>。

