枪手<ref name=IBTimes.Mercer/>'''克里斯托弗·肖恩·哈珀-梅瑟'''（{{lang|en|Christopher Sean Harper-Mercer}}，{{bd|1989年|7月26日||2015年10月1日}}）被认定为枪手。最初有报道称梅瑟并非社区学院的学生<ref name=IBTimes.Mercer>{{cite web|url=http://www.ibtimes.com/who-chris-harper-mercer-oregons-alleged-umqua-community-college-shooter-identified-2123675|title=Who Is Chris Harper Mercer? Oregon's Alleged Umqua Community College Shooter Identified, Police Say|work=IBTimes|date=2015-10-01|accessdate=2015-10-01|archive-date=2015-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151002234847/http://www.ibtimes.com/who-chris-harper-mercer-oregons-alleged-umqua-community-college-shooter-identified-2123675|dead-url=no}}</ref>，只不过是一部即将在学校上映的戏剧的制作助理<ref name=guardianperp>{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2015/oct/02/chris-harper-mercer-first-details-emerge-of-oregon-college-killer|title=Chris Harper Mercer: first details emerge of Oregon college killer|first=Ben|last=Jacobs|work=The Guardian|date=2015-10-02|accessdate=2015-10-02|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308165650/https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2015/oct/02/chris-harper-mercer-first-details-emerge-of-oregon-college-killer|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而，执法人员表示哈珀-梅瑟在案发当天被一个班录取<ref name=KTLA.Enrolled/>。

梅瑟在英国出生，小时候移居美国<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/news/umpqua-community-college-shooting-chris-harper-mercer/|title=What we know about suspected Oregon shooter Chris Harper Mercer|work=CBS News|date=2015-10-01|accessdate=2015-10-01|archive-date=2015-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151002040619/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/umpqua-community-college-shooting-chris-harper-mercer/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2008年11月5日到12月11日，他曾在[[南卡罗来纳州|南卡罗来纳州]][[杰克逊堡|杰克逊堡]]的美军基地服役。退伍他完成了基础训练，但“未能达到最低的管理标准”<ref name=KTLA.Enrolled/><ref name=NYTimes.Hinted>{{cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/10/03/us/chris-harper-mercer-umpqua-community-college-shooting.html|title=Chris Mercer, Oregon Gunman, Hinted of Anger and Loneliness|work=The New York Times|date=2015-10-02|accessdate=2015-10-02|first=Ian|last=Lovett|first2=Liam|last2=Stack|archive-date=2021-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210216161336/https://www.nytimes.com/2015/10/03/us/chris-harper-mercer-umpqua-community-college-shooting.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2010年到2012年，他就读于{{le|艾尔·卡密诺学院|El Camino College}}<ref name=KTLA.Enrolled/>。梅瑟于2011年到2013年与母亲生活在[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[托伦斯_(加利福尼亚州)|托伦斯]]<ref name=HuffPost.Identified/><ref name=dailybeastprofiles/>，从一家专门为有学习障碍或情绪问题的青少年开设的学校斯威策学习中心（{{lang|en|Switzer Learning Center}}）毕业<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailybulletin.com/general-news/20151001/oregon-shooting-suspect-chris-harper-mercer-lived-in-torrance-graduated-from-switzer-center|title=Oregon shooting suspect lived in Torrance, graduated from Switzer Center|work=The Daily Bulletin|date=2015-10-01|accessdate=2015-10-01}}</ref>。他的母亲被形容溺爱梅瑟，多次努力保护梅瑟不受街区中各种感知烦恼的伤害，其中一些是次要的<ref name=NYTimes.Hinted/>。之后因母亲工作需要，与其共同搬到[[俄勒冈州|俄勒冈州]]{{le|温彻斯特 (俄勒冈州)|Winchester, Oregon|温彻斯特}}<ref name=NYTimes.Hinted/><ref name=HuffPost.Identified>{{cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/oregon-college-shooter-identified_560da1b2e4b0dd85030b5cc3|title=Oregon College Shooter Identified As Chris Harper Mercer|work=Huffington Post|date=2015-10-01|accessdate=2015-10-01|archive-date=2016-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160112082112/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/oregon-college-shooter-identified_560da1b2e4b0dd85030b5cc3|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=dailybeastprofiles/>。

邻居和属人们称梅瑟为了“古怪”“轻佻”。一名邻居称梅瑟“夜里开着小亮光独自坐在阳台上”，而另一名邻居称“他的神态，他走路时总是环顾四周，我都被他的坏情绪影响了<ref name="edpayne,sarasidnerandkyunglah,cnn">{{cite web|url=http://www.cnn.com/2015/10/02/us/oregon-umpqua-community-college-shooting/index.html|title=Umpqua College gunman apparently targeted Christians - CNN.com|author=Ed Payne, Sara Sidner and Kyung Lah, CNN|date=2015-10-02|work=CNN|access-date=2015-10-02|archive-date=2015-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151002202655/http://www.cnn.com/2015/10/02/us/oregon-umpqua-community-college-shooting/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”梅瑟在俄勒冈州的一位邻居表示自己和丈夫在她家阳台抽烟时，梅瑟经常朝她大喊大叫<ref name=NYTimes.Hinted/>。

梅瑟有数个名为“[[铁十字勋章|铁十字]]45”（{{lang|en|Iron Cross 45}}）的网络账号，该名字指[[纳粹德国|纳粹德国]]<ref name=mashableperp>{{cite web|url=http://mashable.com/2015/10/02/chris-harper-mercer-ucc-shooting/|title=Who is Chris Harper-Mercer, the man suspected of killing 9 in Oregon?|author=Jenni Ryall|date=2015-10-02|work=Mashable|access-date=2015-10-02|archive-date=2015-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151003115328/http://mashable.com/2015/10/02/chris-harper-mercer-ucc-shooting/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。梅瑟的电子邮件所连接的[[MySpace|MySpace]]档案有宣传亲[[爱尔兰共和军|爱尔兰共和军]]的内容<ref name=dailybeastprofiles>{{cite web|url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2015/10/01/umpqua-gunman-id-d-as-chris-harper-mercer.html|title=Umpqua Gunman Chris Harper-Mercer Hated Religion Online|work=The Daily Beast|date=2015-10-01|accessdate=2015-10-01|archive-date=2015-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151004182741/http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2015/10/01/umpqua-gunman-id-d-as-chris-harper-mercer.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而在另外一份交友档案中，他表示自己是与父母住在一起的“混血”男子<ref name=mediaite>{{cite web|url=http://www.mediaite.com/online/who-is-alleged-oregon-college-gunman-chris-harper-mercer|title=Who Is Alleged Oregon College Gunman Chris Harper Mercer?|work=Mediaite|date=2015-10-01|accessdate=2015-10-01|archive-date=2020-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123080546/https://www.mediaite.com/online/who-is-alleged-oregon-college-gunman-chris-harper-mercer/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，他的立场是“保守的，共和党人”<ref name="Garcia">{{cite web | url=http://www.rawstory.com/2015/10/umpqua-college-terrorist-identified-as-26-year-old-chris-harper-mercer/ | title=Umpqua College terrorist identified as 26-year-old Chris Harper Mercer: report | publisher=Raw Story | date=2015-10-01 | accessdate=2015-10-01 | last=Garcia | first=Arturo | archive-date=2020-11-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108142242/https://www.rawstory.com/2015/10/umpqua-college-terrorist-identified-as-26-year-old-chris-harper-mercer/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。梅瑟在他的[[BitTorrent|BitTorrent]]账户中上传了一部关于[[桑迪·胡克小学枪击案|桑迪·胡克小学枪击案]]的纪录片<ref name=mashableperp/><ref name=guardianperp/>。

