tps://abcnews.go.com/US/umpqua-community-college-shooter-chris-harper-mercer-hate/story?id=34203754|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation/2015/10/02/oregon-college-shooting/73192562/|title=Official: Oregon gunman left angry note glorifying mass killers|work=USA Today|date=2015-10-02|accessdate=2015-10-02|first=Trevor|last=Hughes|first2=Kevin|last2=Johnson|archive-date=2020-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200810184545/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation/2015/10/02/oregon-college-shooting/73192562/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 经过 ==
太平洋夏令时上午10点38分，第一通[[911|911]]报警电话从校园内打出。一名枪手据报走过数座校舍朝人们胡乱扫射<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/10/02/us/oregon-shooting-umpqua-community-college.html?_r=0|title=Oregon Community College Shooting Leaves at Least 7 Dead|work=The New York Times|date=2015-10-01|accessdate=2015-10-01|archive-date=2021-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210201182730/https://www.nytimes.com/2015/10/02/us/oregon-shooting-umpqua-community-college.html?_r=0|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.katu.com/news/local/Reports-Active-shooter-on-the-Umpqua-Community-College-campus--330285921.html|title=Deadly shooting at Umpqua Community College|publisher=KATU|date=2015-10-01|accessdate=2015-10-01|archive-date=2015-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151016232700/http://www.katu.com/news/local/Reports-Active-shooter-on-the-Umpqua-Community-College-campus--330285921.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。大部分枪击事件发生在斯内德大厅（{{lang|en|Snyder Hall}}）15号房间，房间内当时正进行英语和写作课<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/live/shooting-at-umpqua-community-college/gunman-identified-as-chris-harper-mercer/|title=Mass Shooting at Umpqua Community College in Oregon: Live Updates|work=The New York Times|date=2015-10-01|accessdate=2015-10-01|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126164645/https://www.nytimes.com/live/shooting-at-umpqua-community-college/gunman-identified-as-chris-harper-mercer|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一名女性尝试关上教室大门时胃部多次中枪<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/10/02/us/oregon-shooting-umpqua-community-college.html?_r=0|title=Oregon Shooting at Umpqua College Kills 10, Sheriff Says|work=The New York Times|date=2015-10-01|accessdate=2015-10-02|archive-date=2021-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210201182730/https://www.nytimes.com/2015/10/02/us/oregon-shooting-umpqua-community-college.html?_r=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>。有目击者指出，梅瑟朝他们开枪前曾询问多名学生的宗教信仰<ref name=":0">{{cite web|url=http://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/multiple-casualties-after-shooting-umpqua-community-college-n437051|title=Oregon Shooting: Umpqua Community College Gunman Talked Religion|first=M. Alex|last=Johnson|work=NBC News|date=October 2, 2015|accessdate=2015-10-02|archive-date=2020-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216161017/https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/multiple-casualties-after-shooting-umpqua-community-college-n437051|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其他则表示梅瑟杀了那些称自己是基督徒的学生，而称自己不是的则遭到他的残害<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":1" /><ref name="edpayne,sarasidnerandkyunglah,cnn" />。

有学生身中多枪。[[美国陆军|美国陆军]]退伍军人克里斯·明茨（{{lang|en|Chris Mintz}}）在学院参加体能训练<ref name=NYT.Mintz>{{cite news|last1=Cain Miller|first1=Claire|last2=Wines|first2=Michael|last3=Turkewitz|first3=Julie|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/10/04/us/confusion-horror-and-heroism-in-oregon-shooting.html|title=Confusion, Horror and Heroism In Oregon Shooting|work=The New York Times|date=2015-10-03|accessdate=2015-10-03|archive-date=2021-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210306204140/https://www.nytimes.com/2015/10/04/us/confusion-horror-and-heroism-in-oregon-shooting.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，案发时他跑进图书馆拉响警报，通知人们逃命<ref name=ABC.Mintz>{{cite news|last=Keneally|first=Meghan|url=http://abcnews.go.com/US/hero-umpqua-community-college-student-chris-mintz-speaks/story?id=34201425|title='Hero' Umpqua Community College Student Chris Mintz Speaks After Being Shot 7 Times|work=ABC News|date=2015-10-02|accessdate=2015-10-03|archive-date=2021-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123162052/https://abcnews.go.com/US/hero-umpqua-community-college-student-chris-mintz-speaks/story?id=34201425|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。然而他跑进发生枪击事件的大楼内试图阻止梅瑟进入一间教室。他在站立时中了三枪，倒地时又中了四枪，但幸免于难。家人们称明茨为英雄<ref name="cnn._Chri">{{cite web|title=Chris Mintz, Oregon shooting hero: 'It's my son's birthday today'|last=Melvin|first=Don|work=CNN|date=2015-10-02|accessdate=2015-10-02|url=http://www.cnn.com/2015/10/02/us/oregon-school-shooting-hero/|archive-date=2020-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200722182838/https://www.cnn.com/2015/10/02/us/oregon-school-shooting-hero/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=USAToday.Hero>{{cite web|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation-now/2015/10/02/hero-oregon-community-college-shooter-gun-violence-massacre/73199764/|title=Hero Chris Mintz shot as he faced Oregon community college shooter|work=USA Today|date=2015-10-02|accessdate=2015-10-02|first=Jessica|last=Durando|first2=Mary|last2=Bowerman|archive-date=2020-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205161504/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation-now/2015/10/02/hero-oregon-community-college-shooter-gun-violence-massacre/73199764/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://abcnews.go.com/US/hero-umpqua-community-college-student-chris-mintz-speaks/story?id=34201425|title='Hero' Umpqua Community College Student Chris Mintz Speaks After Being Shot 7 Times|work=ABC News|date=2015-10-02|accessdate=2015-10-02|first=Meghan|last=Keneally|archive-date=2021-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123162052/https://abcnews.go.com/US/hero-umpqua-community-college-student-chris-mintz-speaks/story?id=34201425|dead-url=no}}</ref>；在10月3日的新闻发布会上，道格拉斯县治安官约翰·翰林为明茨作出的行为表示感谢<ref name=WP.thanks>{{cite news|last1=Shapiro|first1=T. Rees|last2=Dewey|first2=Caitlyn|last3=Bernstein|first3=Lenny|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/national/oregon-shooter-killed-himself-after-2-officers-arrived-at-community-college/2015/10/03/92f02542-6a05-11e5-8325-a42b5a459b1e_story.html|title=Oregon shooter killed himself after 3 officers arrived at community college|work=The Washington Post|date=2015-10-03|accessdate=2015-10-03|archive-date=2015-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151003201241/https://www.washingtonpost.com/national/oregon-shooter-killed-himself-after-2-officers-arrived-at-community-college/2015/10/03/92f02542-6a05-11e5-8325-a42b5a459b1e_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。明茨的家人设立了一个GoFundMe帐户来支付明茨的医疗费用，截至10月2日，帐户受到超过65万美元的捐款<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.kgw.com/story/news/local/roseburg-college-shooting/2015/10/02/hero-shot-7-times-standing-up-roseburg-shooter/73205662/|title=Over $650K raised for hero shot 7 times standing up to shooter|publisher=KGW|date=2015-10-03|accessdate=2015-10-03|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151004000301/http://www.kgw.com/story/news/local/roseburg-college-shooting/2015/10/02/hero-shot-7-times-standing-up-roseburg-shooter/73205662/|archivedate=2015-10-04|df=}}</ref>。

枪手在与赶往现场的警察的枪战中被击毙，所幸无警察受伤。<ref name=Ford>{{cite news|last1=Ford|first1=Dana|title=Oregon shooting: Gunman dead after college rampage|url=http://www.cnn.com/2015/10/01/us/oregon-college-shooting/index.html|accessdate=2015-10-01|publisher=CNN|date=2015-10-01|archive-date=2015-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151001183945/http://www.cnn.com/2015/10/01/us/oregon-college-shooting/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=KGW.Shooting>{{cite web|url=http://www.kgw.com/story/news/crime/2015/10/01/report-15-dead-umpqua-community-college-shooting/73154898/|title=13 dead at community college school shooting near Roseburg, officials say|publisher=KGW|date=2015-10-01|accessdate=2015-10-01|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151001224238/http://www.kgw.com/story/news/crime/2015/10/01/report-15-dead-umpqua-community-college-shooting/73154898/|archivedate=2015-10-01}}</ref><ref name=KOIN.Among/><ref name=KTLA.ID>{{cite web|url=http://ktla.com/2015/10/01/gunman-in-oregon-college-shooting-that-left-10-dead-idd/|title=Former L.A. County Resident ID'd as Gunman in Umpqua Community College Shooting That Left 10 Dead: Report|work=KTLA|date=2015-10-01|accessdate=2015-10-01|first=Tracy|last=Bloom|archive-date=2015-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151002040353/http://ktla.com/2015/10/01/gunman-in-oregon-college-shooting-that-left-10-dead-idd/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://pix11.com/2015/10/02/father-of-oregon-shooting-victim-gunman-singled-out-christians|title=Father of Oregon shooting victim: Gunman singled out Christians|work=PIX11|date=2015-10-01|accessdate=2015-10-01|archive-date=2019-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191221210718/https://pix11.com/2015/10/02/father-of-oregon-shooting-victim-gunman-singled-out-christians/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

案发后，[[美国烟酒枪炮及爆裂物管理局|美国烟酒枪炮及爆裂物管理局]]特工在校园寻找爆炸物，共从现场检获包括三把[[手枪|手枪和]]一支[[长枪|长枪在内的四把武器]]<ref name=Ford/><ref>{{cite news |url= http://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2015/oct/1/chris-harper-mercer-identified-umpqua-community-co/ |accessdate= 2015-10-01 |title= Chris Harper Mercer identified as Umpqua Community College shooter |newspaper= The Washington Times |archive-date= 2015-10-02 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20151002204337/http://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2015/oct/1/chris-harper-mercer-identified-umpqua-community-co/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>。执法人员表示，枪手身着[[防弹衣|防弹衣]]，“弹药足以用于长时间的枪战”<ref name=KTLA.ID/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://abcnews.go.com/US/umpqua-community-college-shooter-armed-guns-flak-jacket/story?id=34191422|title=Umpqua Community College Shooter Armed With 6 Guns and Flak Jacket|work=ABC News|date=2015-10-02|accessdate=2015-10-02|first=Meghan|last=Keneally|archive-date=2021-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210210162454/https://abcnews.go.com/US/umpqua-community-college-shooter-armed-guns-flak-jacket/story?id=34191422|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他们在梅瑟的公寓房还发现了另外的七把枪，这些枪都是梅瑟的家人合法购买的<ref name="CCM">{{cite web|first=Claire Cain|last=Miller|first2=Richard|last2=Pérez-Peña|first3=Michael S.|last3=Schmidt|date=2015-10-02|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/10/03/us/oregon-shooting-umpqua-chris-harper-mercer.html?_r=0|title=Gunman in Oregon Shooting Was Armed With 6 Guns and Left 7 at Home|work=The New York Times|accessdate=2015-10-02|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108100202/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/10/03/us/oregon-shooting-umpqua-chris-harper-mercer.html?_r=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 受害者 ==
除枪手外，共有九名在枪击案中遇害，死者包括八名学生和一名讲师。另有九人受伤，有伤者遭受多处枪伤后。四名伤者在梅西医疗中心（{{lang|en|Mercy Medical Center}}）接受治疗，一名伤者情况危殆，其余三个情况稳定。其余三名幸存者被转往[[斯普林菲尔德_(俄勒冈州)|斯普林菲尔德]]的平安健康圣心医院（{{lang|en|PeaceHealth Sacred Heart Hospital}}），其中一人危殆，其余两人随后出院<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/oregon-college-shooting-alleged-gunman-id-d-as-chris-harper-mercer-26-1.3252645|title=Oregon college shooting: Alleged gunman ID'd as Chris Harper Mercer, 26|work=CBC News|date=2015-10-01|accessdate=2015-10-01|archive-date=2015-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151002182552/http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/oregon-college-shooting-alleged-gunman-id-d-as-chris-harper-mercer-26-1.3252645|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://registerguard.com/rg/news/local/33566342-75/10-dead-7-injured-in-shooting-at-umpqua-community-college-in-roseburg-gunman-dead.html.csp|title=10 dead, 7 injured in shooting at Umpqua Community College in Roseburg; gunman dead|work=The Register-Guard|date=2015-10-01|accessdate=2015-10-01}}</ref>。

一名死者是俄勒冈州[[美国参议院|参议员]][[杰夫·默克利|杰夫·默克利]]的表弟<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.oregonlive.com/mapes/index.ssf/2015/10/jeff_merkley_says_a_cousin_die.html|title=Jeff Merkley: Relative died in Umpqua college shooting|publisher=OregonLive|date=2015-10-02|accessdate=2015-10-02|archive-date=2019-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190114210739/https://www.oregonlive.com/mapes/index.ssf/2015/10/jeff_merkley_says_a_cousin_die.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.oregonlive.com/politics/index.ssf/2015/10/jeff_merkley_relative_lost_in.html?hootPostID=716ca487c1c6f9f98d13e20df9c39df3#incart_river_home|title=Jeff Merkley: Relative lost in shooting was 'beautiful spirit'|publisher=OregonLive|date=2015-10-02|accessdate=2015-10-02|archive-date=2018-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180103011706/http://www.oregonlive.com/politics/index.ssf/2015/10/jeff_merkley_relative_lost_in.html?hootPostID=716ca487c1c6f9f98d13e20df9c39df3#incart_river_home|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 反应 ==
[[File:The_President_Delivers_a_Statement_on_the_Shooting_in_Oregon.webm|thumb]]

[[美国总统|美国总统]][[贝拉克·奥巴马|贝拉克·奥巴马当天]]事件发表声明要求更严格的枪支法律，因为“（思念和祈祷）不能表达我们应该感到的心痛、悲伤和愤怒；它们也无法阻止这种惨案下周或几月后在美国其他地方发生。”他还称美国对大规模枪击案变得麻木起来。

俄勒冈州州长凯特·布朗（{{lang|en|Kate Brown}}）表示她对事件感到伤心欲绝，并动身前往罗斯堡<ref name="Obamastatement" />。

美国社区学院协会（{{lang|en|American Association of Community Colleges}}）和社区学院理事协会（{{lang|en|Association of Community College Trustees}}）发表联合声明称枪击案为一桩悲剧，并表示将致力于校园安全工作<ref name="NBC" />。

道格拉斯县警长约翰·翰林（{{lang|en|John Hanlin}}）拒说出梅瑟的名字，他表示：“我不会谈枪手……我不会把他归功于这个可怕的懦夫行为。媒体到时候会得到被证实的名字的……但你是永远不会听到我们说他的名字的<ref name=":1">{{cite news|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2015/10/02/oregon-shooter-said-to-have-singled-out-christians-for-killing-in-horrific-act-of-cowardice/|title=Oregon shooter said to have singled out Christians for killing in ‘horrific act of cowardice’|publisher=The Washington Post|date=2015-10-02|accessdate=2015-10-02|archive-date=2021-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211042610/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2015/10/02/oregon-shooter-said-to-have-singled-out-christians-for-killing-in-horrific-act-of-cowardice/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”

案发后，联邦当局调查了案发前日[[4chan|4chan]]上的一篇帖子，这个网站因能用假名发布恶作剧和挑衅性评论而著称。这篇帖子警告称：“你们这些家伙还好。如果你住在西北部，明天别去上学<ref>{{cite web|url=https://archive.moe/r9k/thread/22785073/#22785073|title=External archive of 4chan discussion thread|work=4chan|accessdate=2015-10-01|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151001192821/https://archive.moe/r9k/thread/22785073/#22785073|archivedate=2015-10-01}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/national/probe-in-college-slayings-peers-into-web-rants-and-possible-religious-rage/2015/10/02/d250007a-68ea-11e5-8325-a42b5a459b1e_story.html|title=Probe in college slayings peers into Web rants and possible religious rage|first=Joseph|last=Hoyt|first2=Sarah|last2=Kaplan|first3=Eli|last3=Saslow|publisher=The Washington Post|date=2015-10-02|accessdate=2015-10-02|archive-date=2018-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180504155739/https://www.washingtonpost.com/national/probe-in-college-slayings-peers-into-web-rants-and-possible-religious-rage/2015/10/02/d250007a-68ea-11e5-8325-a42b5a459b1e_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”同时，[[BuzzFeed|BuzzFeed]]的全球新闻总监发布推特称“4chan的成员设立虚假的记者及媒体组织[[Twitter|Twitter]]账户发布假的嫌犯消息<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.ibtimes.com/who-oregons-umpqua-cc-shooter-4chan-users-reportedly-create-fake-gunman-twitter-2123576|title=Who Is Oregon’s Umpqua CC Shooter? 4Chan Users Reportedly Create Fake Gunman Twitter Accounts|publisher=IBTimes|first=Maria|last=Vultagglio|date=2015-10-02|accessdate=2015-10-02|archive-date=2019-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191130185626/https://www.ibtimes.com/who-oregons-umpqua-cc-shooter-4chan-users-reportedly-create-fake-gunman-twitter-2123576|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。”[[BBC|BBC]]表示，本案是2015年美国发生的第45起校园枪击案，也是自2012年[[桑迪·胡克小学枪击案|桑迪·胡克小学枪击案]]以来的第142起<ref name="BBC News 2 October 2015">{{cite web| title= Oregon shooting: Statistics behind 'routine' US gun violence| url= http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-us-canada-34424385| date= 2015-10-02| website= BBC News Online| accessdate= 2015-10-02| archive-date= 2021-03-08| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210308052421/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-us-canada-34424385| dead-url= no}}</ref>。

